I'm just wanted to add this because...well...people need to know. When cd's sell, bands don't see that money. They've already been paid. The only money bands see on a regular basis is from touring. The money from cd's goes towards just about everything else except the band. A minute amount goes to the band. If you want to support a band, don't buy their cd's. Go to their shows.
